WEBVTT

00:00:13.347 --> 00:00:15.015
Hey, Child Emperor...

00:00:16.558 --> 00:00:17.809
Can I ask you something?

00:00:18.435 --> 00:00:20.478
If you're hungry, you'll have to wait.

00:00:20.479 --> 00:00:22.105
Not that!

00:00:22.564 --> 00:00:23.981
After we escape from here

00:00:23.982 --> 00:00:26.692
you'll make sure to take me
to my dad, right?

00:00:26.693 --> 00:00:28.903
No, I can't go that far with you.

00:00:28.904 --> 00:00:33.199
The other heroes on the surface will
take over to protect you, so don't worry.

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:34.867
The other heroes?

00:00:34.868 --> 00:00:36.410
You mean they're not Class-S?

00:00:36.411 --> 00:00:38.955
What?! No way!
They gotta be Class-S.

00:00:38.956 --> 00:00:40.499
No way.

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.501
You saw me fighting, right?

00:00:43.502 --> 00:00:44.877
The enemy is strong.

00:00:44.878 --> 00:00:47.840
I have to get back to the battlefield
right away and support everyone.

00:00:49.716 --> 00:00:51.218
I'm worried about them.

00:00:52.261 --> 00:00:55.305
They don't know how to cooperate.

00:00:56.098 --> 00:00:58.100
So someone has to
be there to lead them.

00:01:00.644 --> 00:01:02.854
You're just a kid
and you're the leader?

00:01:02.855 --> 00:01:04.273
But they're all adults.

00:01:06.441 --> 00:01:08.776
Honestly, I wish someone else
would take over.

00:01:08.777 --> 00:01:09.611
But...
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:01:10.863 --> 00:01:13.740
Sorry, this isn't the time
to get into that.

00:01:14.324 --> 00:01:17.119
Don't worry.
I'm the class president, too.

00:01:18.203 --> 00:01:19.872
Although I don't go to school much.

00:01:20.455 --> 00:01:22.916
Look! We're almost at the exit.

00:01:23.458 --> 00:01:25.293
Come on, let's go. Waganma.

00:01:25.294 --> 00:01:27.546
Oh... Okay.

00:01:28.463 --> 00:01:29.506
You're right.

00:01:34.928 --> 00:01:38.472
Power to The People

00:01:38.473 --> 00:01:43.729
With my mighty arm
I'll bring this to an end

00:01:48.483 --> 00:01:52.278
It's my Turn!

00:01:52.279 --> 00:01:54.405
Here we go again

00:01:54.406 --> 00:01:56.574
We swarm the Association as a pack!

00:01:56.575 --> 00:01:57.700
Dangerous to the max

00:01:57.701 --> 00:01:59.243
Already at the limit

00:01:59.244 --> 00:02:01.537
It can't get any worse! But...

00:02:01.538 --> 00:02:03.664
Oh oh oh oh oh

00:02:03.665 --> 00:02:05.917
Victory isn't about numbers

00:02:05.918 --> 00:02:08.211
Hi hi hi hi hi

00:02:08.212 --> 00:02:10.546
Show time
Let's turn it up!

00:02:10.547 --> 00:02:18.804
Overcome every trial
thrown at you by the heavens

00:02:18.805 --> 00:02:22.893
Raise the fist of fire!

00:02:23.185 --> 00:02:25.687
Stand up and fight
That's what you call a hero!

00:02:25.979 --> 00:02:27.438
Anytime, anywhere

00:02:27.439 --> 00:02:32.235
Crush all the evil monsters that attack!

00:02:32.236 --> 00:02:37.031
Come on, more (more), more (more)
I need the rush

00:02:37.032 --> 00:02:41.453
This isn't enough
No satisfied yeah!

00:02:41.828 --> 00:02:45.874
Just be stronger than anyone, anyone
Hey!

00:02:46.291 --> 00:02:50.337
Dance, dance across the sky
of destruction! Hey!

00:02:50.712 --> 00:02:55.008
Always, always finish it in one blow!

00:02:55.884 --> 00:02:59.388
One Punch!

00:03:00.055 --> 00:03:03.767
(Top Dragons)

00:03:05.686 --> 00:03:06.854
This is Child Emperor.

00:03:07.396 --> 00:03:10.314
I've successfully linked up with
the surface team along with Waganma.

00:03:10.315 --> 00:03:12.733
The rescue operation was a success!

00:03:12.734 --> 00:03:15.320
I repeat.
The rescue operation was a success!

00:03:16.029 --> 00:03:19.240
Child Emperor...
You are seriously incredible.

00:03:19.241 --> 00:03:21.701
Yes, your execution was flawless.

00:03:21.702 --> 00:03:25.037
You only think that because you didn't see
what happened out there.

00:03:25.038 --> 00:03:26.623
We barely made it out alive.

00:03:27.666 --> 00:03:29.750
No one's responding.

00:03:29.751 --> 00:03:32.087
Hello, is anyone listening?

00:03:33.714 --> 00:03:36.299
Are my messages getting through?

00:03:36.300 --> 00:03:39.136
Or even if they are,
is anyone actually checking them?

00:03:39.970 --> 00:03:42.014
Come on,
can we wrap this up already...

00:03:43.182 --> 00:03:49.437
Sekingal, I did explain
how to use the transmitters, right?

00:03:49.438 --> 00:03:52.481
Including checking
notifications regularly?

00:03:52.482 --> 00:03:56.861
Easy now, they might be
too busy fighting to look.

00:03:56.862 --> 00:03:58.322
This is Zombieman.

00:03:59.153 --> 00:04:01.283
Good job, Child Emperor.

00:04:01.742 --> 00:04:02.868
It's Zombieman...

00:04:03.577 --> 00:04:05.161
This is Amai Mask.

00:04:05.162 --> 00:04:09.166
Got it about the hostage.
The monsters are no big deal.

00:04:09.744 --> 00:04:12.163
I will continue to carry out justice.

00:04:12.164 --> 00:04:13.934
Good job, Child Emperor.

00:04:13.935 --> 00:04:16.546
This is Pig God.
I am currently digesting.

00:04:17.910 --> 00:04:19.619
Hm? What's this?

00:04:19.620 --> 00:04:21.897
So I press here and talk?

00:04:21.898 --> 00:04:23.257
It's Atomic Samurai!

00:04:24.890 --> 00:04:27.558
What's this green flashing light?

00:04:27.559 --> 00:04:29.144
That's my message.

00:04:29.852 --> 00:04:33.355
Let's see now.
If I press here...

00:04:33.356 --> 00:04:35.215
Oh, the light went off.

00:04:35.216 --> 00:04:38.244
Oh! He deleted it. Geez.

00:04:39.738 --> 00:04:42.156
Ahh, this is Atomic Samurai.

00:04:42.157 --> 00:04:46.077
Well, everyone... If you have time,
listen to this message.

00:04:46.078 --> 00:04:48.037
I found a child.

00:04:48.038 --> 00:04:48.996
What?

00:04:48.997 --> 00:04:51.874
The location is...
Hmm, where am I...?

00:04:51.875 --> 00:04:54.544
Well, never mind.
I'll go after him.

00:04:54.545 --> 00:04:57.673
Hello? This is Child Emperor.
What child?

00:04:58.257 --> 00:04:59.716
We lost the connection.

00:05:01.176 --> 00:05:02.135
Waganma.

00:05:03.470 --> 00:05:04.805
Do you know about this?

00:05:05.556 --> 00:05:07.891
So there was another person
held captive?

00:05:08.475 --> 00:05:12.228
Um... Well... So...

00:05:12.229 --> 00:05:13.694
You knew about it?

00:05:13.695 --> 00:05:17.275
Y-Yeah... B-But...
I just wanted to be saved...

00:05:17.276 --> 00:05:19.861
I'm s-s-sorry! Sorry!

00:05:19.862 --> 00:05:21.071
I have to go.

00:05:21.738 --> 00:05:25.533
Sekingal and the surface team.
Please take care of Waganma.

00:05:25.534 --> 00:05:27.994
Huh? Don't tell me
you're going back down there?

00:05:27.995 --> 00:05:29.328
Child Emperor!

00:05:29.329 --> 00:05:32.582
You look exhausted.
Can you still keep going?

00:05:32.583 --> 00:05:36.210
Rescuing Waganma was our priority,
and we've accomplished that.

00:05:36.211 --> 00:05:37.921
Perhaps it's best to reset...

00:05:40.799 --> 00:05:43.009
You don't get it, suit guy.

00:05:43.010 --> 00:05:46.012
Now that we know,
we got no choice but to go.

00:05:46.013 --> 00:05:47.597
I'll help too.

00:05:47.598 --> 00:05:49.098
Let us join you too.

00:05:49.099 --> 00:05:50.684
No, that isn't necessary.

00:05:51.727 --> 00:05:53.729
Let us each fulfill
our respective roles.

00:05:54.980 --> 00:05:55.981
Class-S...

00:05:56.324 --> 00:06:00.412
I want to reach that level someday,
but it won't be easy.

00:06:01.987 --> 00:06:04.447
You came outta nowhere
and tried to cut me.

00:06:04.448 --> 00:06:06.490
You trying to pick a fight?

00:06:06.491 --> 00:06:12.079
The hard-boiled, yet compassionate hero,
Atomic Samurai, has arrived!

00:06:12.080 --> 00:06:14.457
Some arrival...

00:06:14.458 --> 00:06:15.166
So you're the Atomic Samurai
Gyoro-Gyoro was talking about.

00:06:15.167 --> 00:06:18.461
(Threat Level Dragon: Black Sperm) So you're the
Atomic Samurai Gyoro-Gyoro was talking about.

00:06:18.462 --> 00:06:19.337
(Threat Level Dragon: Black Sperm)

00:06:19.338 --> 00:06:23.174
You don't look like much, but whatever.
(Threat Level Dragon: Black Sperm)

00:06:23.175 --> 00:06:26.469
I've been bored out of my mind. Entertain
me. (Threat Level Dragon: Black Sperm)

00:06:26.470 --> 00:06:27.637
Oh yeah?

00:06:27.638 --> 00:06:29.722
But I've got no business with you.

00:06:29.723 --> 00:06:31.808
You're underestimating me, aren't you?

00:06:36.855 --> 00:06:37.772
Hmm.

00:06:37.773 --> 00:06:39.732
You underestimate me.

00:06:39.733 --> 00:06:43.237
Yeah. To be blunt,
this is going to be a piece of cake.

00:06:46.323 --> 00:06:48.492
I've been through countless battles.

00:06:48.944 --> 00:06:53.372
I've sliced up dozens of mutated,
gigantic freaks like you.

00:06:53.872 --> 00:06:55.207
I'm used to it by now.

00:06:58.961 --> 00:07:01.587
So you're the type
that can split up, huh?

00:07:01.588 --> 00:07:04.090
The most annoying kind.

00:07:04.091 --> 00:07:06.969
Annoying? You're a fool.

00:07:07.344 --> 00:07:09.011
You still think you can win?

00:07:09.012 --> 00:07:12.349
I'm a mass of countless versions of me.

00:07:12.698 --> 00:07:16.701
No matter how much you cut,
rip, beat, crush, or twist me

00:07:16.702 --> 00:07:18.270
I just keep multiplying.

00:07:19.940 --> 00:07:21.191
You're the fool.

00:07:21.733 --> 00:07:25.570
I'll just unleash countless slashes
on all of you and win.

00:07:25.571 --> 00:07:28.240
Do it if you can.
I'll make you weep.

00:07:28.657 --> 00:07:30.742
Come on, bring it on.
Let's do this.

00:07:50.929 --> 00:07:52.222
Atomic...

00:07:53.056 --> 00:07:54.016
Slash!!

00:07:56.148 --> 00:07:59.151
It's over. You're dead.

00:08:01.523 --> 00:08:02.565
What the...?!

00:08:02.566 --> 00:08:05.777
He has this much power
even after splitting up?

00:08:06.566 --> 00:08:08.362
I underestimated him.

00:08:08.363 --> 00:08:09.865
This is bad, there's too many!

00:08:29.621 --> 00:08:32.165
- So Gyoro-Gyoro had it figured out.
- It's no use.

00:08:32.166 --> 00:08:35.777
- Just accept it.
- We're the worst possible match for you.

00:08:35.778 --> 00:08:38.137
Heh. I'll bury you.

00:08:40.771 --> 00:08:41.855
The ceiling?!

00:08:44.983 --> 00:08:46.235
That shaking...

00:08:48.153 --> 00:08:49.946
I wonder how the battle is going.

00:08:49.947 --> 00:08:51.698
So you're worried?

00:08:51.699 --> 00:08:53.908
About how the other heroes
are getting killed?

00:08:53.909 --> 00:08:54.910
How did you...?

00:08:59.289 --> 00:09:01.999
Maybe they died like this?

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:04.710
(Threat Level: Dragon Homeless Emperor) Dying
instantly without even being able to resist.

00:09:04.711 --> 00:09:08.172
So this is how
a so-called hero dies?

00:09:08.173 --> 00:09:09.716
How pathetic.

00:09:10.509 --> 00:09:13.719
I checked out the Hero Association's
official website.

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:16.722
The Class-S heroes that are left...

00:09:16.723 --> 00:09:20.393
can easily by annihilated by just me!

00:09:20.394 --> 00:09:20.936
Wait!

00:09:39.079 --> 00:09:40.830
That looks painful.

00:09:40.831 --> 00:09:43.000
Blocked at that range?!

00:09:44.793 --> 00:09:48.172
Tsk. I was saving this for last...

00:10:00.225 --> 00:10:03.561
As expected of one of the top heroes.

00:10:03.562 --> 00:10:06.022
Even in death, you refuse to fall.

00:10:06.023 --> 00:10:08.233
You must have been quite strong.

00:10:08.734 --> 00:10:13.112
Yeah. I don't need a suit that
can withstand heavy bombing

00:10:13.113 --> 00:10:15.448
armor that can deflect bullets

00:10:15.449 --> 00:10:19.077
or an invincible shield that repels
any kind of physical attack.

00:10:19.703 --> 00:10:21.663
All I need is a spare change of clothes.

00:10:22.289 --> 00:10:25.000
And above all, I'm very particular
about my boxer shorts.

00:10:25.584 --> 00:10:28.544
I have no overwhelming power,
no superior physical ability

00:10:28.545 --> 00:10:31.047
no devastating weapons.

00:10:31.048 --> 00:10:33.799
The only thing I need to win
a battle is...

00:10:33.800 --> 00:10:36.637
The resolve to fight completely naked.

00:10:37.221 --> 00:10:40.515
And that's why boxer shorts
are non-negotiable for me.

00:10:40.516 --> 00:10:41.974
What are you talking about?

00:10:41.975 --> 00:10:44.558
Seriously though,
this is no laughing matter.

00:10:44.559 --> 00:10:46.188
This monster is too strong.

00:10:47.606 --> 00:10:48.439
Hey.

00:10:48.440 --> 00:10:52.778
I can't figure out that sneaky,
trick-like attack of yours.

00:10:53.403 --> 00:10:54.779
What the hell are you?

00:10:54.780 --> 00:10:56.864
I'm surprised.

00:10:56.865 --> 00:10:59.325
They don't call you Zombieman
for nothing.

00:10:59.326 --> 00:11:03.205
Being immortal wasn't just
a figure of speech, huh?

00:11:03.872 --> 00:11:07.125
So you want to know
the secret of this light's power?

00:11:07.835 --> 00:11:12.380
Fine... I'll tell you how
I acquired this power.

00:11:12.381 --> 00:11:16.760
Until a month ago, I stayed at a park,
living day by day.

00:11:18.095 --> 00:11:20.721
I lost my job and got kicked out
of my home.

00:11:20.722 --> 00:11:25.059
I left human society behind
and lived as a recluse.

00:11:25.060 --> 00:11:26.853
At a welcome party
for new employees

00:11:26.854 --> 00:11:30.038
my boss ordered me
to dance naked.

00:11:30.039 --> 00:11:33.025
The next day,
I was fired for sexual harassment.

00:11:33.986 --> 00:11:35.945
But when I looked up at the sky

00:11:35.946 --> 00:11:39.283
my resentment toward
my boss no longer mattered.

00:11:39.825 --> 00:11:42.368
The Earth is bigger than any building

00:11:42.369 --> 00:11:44.872
and the sky is brighter than
any man-made light.

00:11:45.455 --> 00:11:48.292
Humans are but insignificant beings.

00:11:48.750 --> 00:11:52.588
My home is this vast Earth itself.

00:11:52.963 --> 00:11:54.923
And then it hit me...

00:11:55.716 --> 00:12:00.219
Humans have strayed from
the natural order of Mother Earth

00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:03.931
abandoning it to flourish selfishly
under our own rules.

00:12:03.932 --> 00:12:06.059
The stupidity of humans is staggering.

00:12:06.894 --> 00:12:09.061
This is outrageous.

00:12:09.062 --> 00:12:13.358
To think these ignorant beings
treat me as inferior!

00:12:14.443 --> 00:12:15.819
It's unbearable.

00:12:16.904 --> 00:12:18.280
Just unbearable.

00:12:18.864 --> 00:12:20.489
So unbearable.

00:12:20.490 --> 00:12:23.034
Humanity, with its shallow intelligence

00:12:23.035 --> 00:12:26.078
built this ugly, tiny,
and foolish world...

00:12:26.079 --> 00:12:31.418
To break free from it and
to truly return to Mother Earth...

00:12:32.794 --> 00:12:35.047
I had no choice
but to choose death.

00:12:36.256 --> 00:12:37.591
And that's when it happened.

00:12:39.468 --> 00:12:42.554
God appeared before my eyes.

00:12:43.844 --> 00:12:45.636
You are correct.

00:12:45.637 --> 00:12:50.375
Humans are fools.
But you do not need to die.

00:12:50.979 --> 00:12:52.898
I shall grant you power.

00:12:53.607 --> 00:12:56.860
You already know what
you must to do with that power.

00:12:58.278 --> 00:13:02.823
In other words, this was a divine power,
given to me by God.

00:13:02.824 --> 00:13:06.828
And of course, I was chosen
because I know the answer.

00:13:07.630 --> 00:13:11.457
Humanity and its foolishness
are a harmful existence to this planet.

00:13:11.458 --> 00:13:13.459
The time has come for me

00:13:13.460 --> 00:13:16.547
to destroy its existence,
its civilization, all of it.

00:13:17.169 --> 00:13:22.219
Oh crap, his story ended
before I could fully regenerate.

00:13:22.970 --> 00:13:26.723
So what made you believe
that guy was actually God?

00:13:27.349 --> 00:13:28.891
Did it have some kind of ID?

00:13:28.892 --> 00:13:31.853
You do not need to believe in God

00:13:31.854 --> 00:13:33.522
and I've heard enough
of your nonsense.

00:13:34.314 --> 00:13:38.735
Atone for your excessive arrogance
by dying and returning to dust.

00:13:40.195 --> 00:13:43.114
Hey, is the ground all right here?

00:13:43.115 --> 00:13:45.158
I hope my place isn't falling apart.

00:13:47.035 --> 00:13:49.788
Maiko Plasma High Voltage Mode.

00:13:50.372 --> 00:13:52.416
Love Lightning Session.

00:13:54.835 --> 00:13:56.336
Take that!

00:13:58.463 --> 00:13:59.548
Did we beat him?

00:14:01.925 --> 00:14:04.051
What's with that pose?!

00:14:04.052 --> 00:14:08.055
Whoa... Class A and Class S
are on a different level...

00:14:08.056 --> 00:14:10.975
We should have had
the advantage in this matchup...

00:14:10.976 --> 00:14:13.604
The special attacks didn't work on him.

00:14:14.062 --> 00:14:16.063
What kind of body does he have?

00:14:16.064 --> 00:14:17.566
Why so surprised?

00:14:18.233 --> 00:14:22.029
I simply embraced the pain with
love deeper than the ocean.

00:14:22.696 --> 00:14:25.698
I call it the Angel Hug.

00:14:25.699 --> 00:14:28.285
- I don't get it.
- Who the hell is this guy?

00:14:28.785 --> 00:14:30.204
We're retreating for now!

00:14:32.414 --> 00:14:33.582
Where are you going?

00:14:34.499 --> 00:14:37.543
(Threat Level: Demon Vacuumer) You think Gyoro-Gyoro
and Orochi would approve of you retreating?

00:14:37.544 --> 00:14:38.711
Shut up.

00:14:38.712 --> 00:14:41.923
Then you fight that freak alone.

00:14:41.924 --> 00:14:43.007
- Yeah, do it. -

00:14:43.008 --> 00:14:45.176
Okay, will do.

00:14:45.177 --> 00:14:48.388
But first, I want your powers.

00:14:58.315 --> 00:14:59.816
Monsters killing monsters?

00:15:02.069 --> 00:15:05.405
You have no love... for your comrades.

00:15:06.907 --> 00:15:09.116
I'm done with the appetizers.

00:15:09.117 --> 00:15:11.119
Now for the main dish.

00:15:14.540 --> 00:15:16.374
I can use these superpowers

00:15:16.375 --> 00:15:19.920
however I want until I digest
and excrete them.

00:15:20.420 --> 00:15:25.132
I have more than enough time
to wipe out every last hero.

00:15:25.133 --> 00:15:29.387
Defeat them?
Impossible for someone like you.

00:15:29.388 --> 00:15:31.097
I'm a Class-S hero

00:15:31.098 --> 00:15:34.851
but compared to them,
I'm just an average man.

00:15:34.852 --> 00:15:37.812
Hey, Monster.
Before you go running your mouth

00:15:37.813 --> 00:15:42.525
let's see if you can take care of
this average adult male in front of you.

00:15:42.526 --> 00:15:44.944
What do you mean,
average adult male?

00:15:44.945 --> 00:15:46.446
You're a freak of nature!

00:15:49.241 --> 00:15:52.285
Looks like your body's
already screaming in pain.

00:15:52.286 --> 00:15:53.870
You're trembling...

00:15:53.871 --> 00:15:56.581
The electricity and poison
are taking a toll on you.

00:15:56.582 --> 00:15:58.249
This was bound to happen.

00:15:58.250 --> 00:16:00.793
Embracing the pain?

00:16:00.794 --> 00:16:02.504
It's all just tough talk.

00:16:04.464 --> 00:16:06.299
Your spirit may be tough

00:16:06.300 --> 00:16:08.927
but if your body can't keep up,
then it's pointless.

00:16:14.641 --> 00:16:17.019
What did you do?
What was that?

00:16:18.103 --> 00:16:23.066
Apparently, my love has given
birth to a new style.

00:16:24.568 --> 00:16:27.696
Vibration Angel descended!!

00:16:29.656 --> 00:16:30.615
Huh?

00:16:30.616 --> 00:16:35.245
Vibration Dark Angel Rush!!

00:16:39.416 --> 00:16:42.699
You... You truly are a freak.

00:16:50.010 --> 00:16:51.135
Honey!

00:16:51.136 --> 00:16:52.470
Let's get outta here.

00:16:52.471 --> 00:16:55.139
But what will Gyoro-Gyoro
and Orochi do to us?

00:16:55.140 --> 00:16:56.558
Who cares?

00:16:56.975 --> 00:17:01.647
My whiskers sense a huge earthquake
or even something bigger coming.

00:17:02.272 --> 00:17:06.667
Whoa, even the monsters
think he's a freak.

00:17:06.668 --> 00:17:08.152
Those voices...

00:17:08.153 --> 00:17:11.948
We've tried slitting his throat
so many times and failed every time.

00:17:11.949 --> 00:17:15.952
Never heard of anyone whose skin
can beat a razor except him.

00:17:15.953 --> 00:17:18.079
But today's the day we kill him.

00:17:18.080 --> 00:17:19.413
Prepare yourself.

00:17:19.414 --> 00:17:20.998
The boss of the stinky prison...

00:17:20.999 --> 00:17:26.003
No, our mortal enemy, the Class-S hero,
Puri-Puri Prisoner!

00:17:26.004 --> 00:17:28.923
My honeys who were taken away
by the monsters?!

00:17:28.924 --> 00:17:30.633
Why do you look like that?

00:17:30.634 --> 00:17:32.635
You look like monsters.

00:17:32.636 --> 00:17:34.846
Look who's talking!

00:17:34.847 --> 00:17:37.640
Damn that Monster Association.

00:17:37.641 --> 00:17:40.184
How could they be so cruel
to these helpless boys?

00:17:40.185 --> 00:17:41.863
Hang in there.
I'm coming to save you...!

00:17:43.355 --> 00:17:44.981
Who're you calling helpless?
(Bam) (Pow) (Whack)

00:17:44.982 --> 00:17:46.732
He's so annoying. Get him!
(Bam) (Pow) (Whack)

00:17:46.733 --> 00:17:48.317
Suffer, you piece of trash!!
(Bam) (Pow) (Whack)

00:17:48.318 --> 00:17:50.862
Don't think this'll settle the score!

00:17:50.863 --> 00:17:52.864
We'll go back to the prison later

00:17:52.865 --> 00:17:56.702
and slaughter your friends
and the guards.

00:17:56.952 --> 00:18:01.790
Oh my god.
Monsterization has twisted their hearts.

00:18:02.124 --> 00:18:03.917
Wake up!

00:18:05.083 --> 00:18:07.668
Try to remember those glorious days.

00:18:08.114 --> 00:18:09.365
We ate and slept together.

00:18:09.902 --> 00:18:12.028
We sweated together doing
the same prison work.

00:18:12.029 --> 00:18:14.360
And we all loved each other
so dearly

00:18:14.361 --> 00:18:16.596
and were connected heart to heart.

00:18:16.597 --> 00:18:18.764
We remember.
That's why we're here for revenge!

00:18:18.765 --> 00:18:20.516
You were slacking off
during prison labor.

00:18:20.517 --> 00:18:22.852
Why doesn't anything
get through to this guy?

00:18:22.853 --> 00:18:24.604
I'll save you, no matter what.

00:18:24.605 --> 00:18:25.605
Just trust me.

00:18:25.606 --> 00:18:26.565
He's not listening...

00:18:26.982 --> 00:18:28.649
Once you turn into a monster

00:18:28.650 --> 00:18:30.777
you can never go back
to being a human.

00:18:31.445 --> 00:18:32.988
Too bad, huh?

00:18:33.739 --> 00:18:34.864
(Threat Level: Dragon Nyaan)

00:18:34.865 --> 00:18:35.949
So sleepy... (Threat
Level: Dragon Nyaan)

00:18:36.658 --> 00:18:40.412
My boyfriend's... hand-knit sweater...

00:18:41.121 --> 00:18:42.955
Okay... The rest is up to you, guys.

00:18:42.956 --> 00:18:45.416
Wow, so that's a top ranker...

00:18:45.417 --> 00:18:47.920
All right. This is
our chance to finish him off!

00:18:51.381 --> 00:18:53.050
He's still moving.

00:18:53.467 --> 00:18:57.346
My honeys will never
be human again?

00:18:58.055 --> 00:19:00.516
Heh, you're wrong.

00:19:01.308 --> 00:19:05.269
If your heart is human,
that makes you a true human being.

00:19:05.270 --> 00:19:07.230
I won't give up.

00:19:07.231 --> 00:19:10.107
I'm going to save my boyfriends,
no matter what.

00:19:10.108 --> 00:19:11.984
For love, nothing is impossible!!

00:19:11.985 --> 00:19:13.861
Man, he's not listening.

00:19:13.862 --> 00:19:15.404
And we're not your boyfriends.

00:19:15.405 --> 00:19:16.572
Who cares? Kill him!

00:19:16.573 --> 00:19:17.866
Kill him!

00:19:22.120 --> 00:19:23.621
He feels different?!

00:19:23.622 --> 00:19:24.497
What the...?

00:19:24.498 --> 00:19:26.833
What happened?

00:19:26.834 --> 00:19:28.042
(Rumbling)

00:19:28.043 --> 00:19:29.627
From all the accumulated damage
(Rumbling)

00:19:29.628 --> 00:19:31.879
his survival instincts were awakened
(Rumbling)

00:19:31.880 --> 00:19:33.965
and his body underwent a rapid evolution...
(Rumbling)

00:19:33.966 --> 00:19:34.549
(Rumbling)

00:19:34.550 --> 00:19:35.550
Something like that?
(Rumbling)

00:19:35.551 --> 00:19:38.052
Have I grown angel wings?

00:19:38.053 --> 00:19:39.428
Obviously, it's just body hair.

00:19:39.429 --> 00:19:40.638
You're not an angel!

00:19:40.639 --> 00:19:41.973
Look how long it is!

00:19:41.974 --> 00:19:44.976
I shall call it,
Angel Bristly Armor.

00:19:44.977 --> 00:19:46.477
Knock it off with that pose.

00:19:46.478 --> 00:19:49.730
Now that I've gained defensive power...

00:19:49.731 --> 00:19:54.570
I'll cuddle with my honeys later
and go after that cat first.

00:19:55.696 --> 00:19:57.447
I can't stand him.

00:19:57.739 --> 00:19:59.616
This feeling reminds me of...

00:20:00.117 --> 00:20:03.828
My former owner forcing
her affection on me.

00:20:03.829 --> 00:20:05.288
Oh well, whatever.

00:20:05.289 --> 00:20:07.541
I'll leave him to the other top rankers.

00:20:08.667 --> 00:20:09.877
Through a gap like that?!

00:20:12.329 --> 00:20:16.216
Give me three millimeters and
I can slip through any gap.

00:20:16.592 --> 00:20:19.844
So I'll go after another hero. Bye!

00:20:19.845 --> 00:20:22.555
Hey, Prisoner.
We're gonna kill you...

00:20:22.556 --> 00:20:23.682
You're not getting away!

00:20:24.641 --> 00:20:26.559
Angel Crawl!

00:20:26.560 --> 00:20:28.896
I'll swim underground and chase
that cat monster.

00:20:30.189 --> 00:20:32.023
Doesn't make sense.

00:20:32.024 --> 00:20:33.232
Meow?!

00:20:33.233 --> 00:20:35.443
I can sense him approaching.

00:20:35.444 --> 00:20:37.613
I instinctively detest this guy.

00:20:38.258 --> 00:20:43.492
I live a selfish existence.
I only fight who I want.

00:20:43.493 --> 00:20:45.453
I'll chase you to
the ends of the earth.

00:20:45.454 --> 00:20:46.538
He's too much for me!

00:20:48.790 --> 00:20:50.917
Oh, you came back, Nyaan?

00:20:50.918 --> 00:20:52.503
Did you finish off Prisoner?

00:21:05.140 --> 00:21:06.432
That cat...

00:21:06.433 --> 00:21:08.769
He said he'll go after other heroes...

00:21:10.229 --> 00:21:11.855
but he doesn't get it.

00:21:12.231 --> 00:21:13.857
I bet he'll regret it.

00:21:14.483 --> 00:21:16.776
He'll soon realize that
going up against me

00:21:16.777 --> 00:21:18.737
would've been the better choice.

00:21:20.697 --> 00:21:22.324
They got caught in the crossfire!

00:21:22.774 --> 00:21:24.317
My boyfriends!

00:21:32.626 --> 00:21:36.505
I'll take this new attack
as a gift from all of you.

00:21:37.172 --> 00:21:38.966
Thank you, my honeys.

00:21:39.883 --> 00:21:41.969
I won't let your sacrifices be in vain.

00:21:42.469 --> 00:21:45.180
Please watch over me in this battle.

00:21:46.306 --> 00:21:47.641
Damn you...

00:21:53.897 --> 00:21:56.024
So it finally stopped, huh?

00:21:57.067 --> 00:22:00.153
What an awful, disgusting sound.

00:22:01.071 --> 00:22:04.532
Yet there was something
kind of sad about it.

00:22:04.533 --> 00:22:05.826
What the heck was that?

00:22:07.202 --> 00:22:09.830
Was it like the gates of hell
opening up or something?

00:22:11.248 --> 00:22:14.543
But seriously, what is this place?
It's ridiculously huge.

00:22:15.294 --> 00:22:17.671
I shoulda asked
those perverts for directions.

00:22:19.298 --> 00:22:20.506
All right.

00:22:20.507 --> 00:22:22.884
Next time I spot someone
who looks like they live here

00:22:22.885 --> 00:22:24.761
I'll grab them and
make them guide me.

00:22:46.325 --> 00:22:56.292
Floating in the same moment
at the edge of righteousness

00:22:56.293 --> 00:23:06.010
If your feelings are wandering alone

00:23:06.011 --> 00:23:12.809
I'll greet them
with the same familiar face

00:23:14.019 --> 00:23:18.981
If the light that shines there

00:23:18.982 --> 00:23:26.280
Illuminates all of us equally now

00:23:26.281 --> 00:23:36.165
Embrace the pain and solitude
just as they are

00:23:36.166 --> 00:23:44.633
With a wish burning in my heart,
I'll press forward

00:23:56.030 --> 00:24:00.993
(Ultimate Lifeform)